.Dd 21/12/23               \" DATE
.Dt man_simple_shell     \" Program name and manual section number
.Os Ubuntu
.Sh NAME                 \" Section Header - required - don't modify
.Nm Simple_shell
.\" The following lines are read in generating the apropos(man -k) database. Use only key
.\" words here as the database is built based on the words here and in the .ND line.
.Nm - Simplified Shell
.Sh SYNOPSIS
simple_shell

.Sh DESCRIPTION
Simple_shell is a simplified version of the shell linux. 
The simple shell utility is a command language interpreter that shall execute commands read from a command line string, the standard input, or a specified file.

.Sh ENVIRONNEMENT VARIABLE
PATH

.Sh MODES AND RUN
.b
Non-interactive mode
 ./hsh [command] [options]

.i
Interactive mode
 ($) /bin/ls

.Sh EXAMPLES
/bin/ls

